{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_32","type":"agent_message","text":"`ReflectionNavigator.loadObjectFactory` uses `ClassLoader.loadClass(\"<package>.ObjectFactory\")`. In native image that means the user-side `ObjectFactory` class must be registered explicitly; otherwise the image excludes it and the library gets `ClassNotFoundException`. I’m checking how this repo models that case in adjacent JAXB tests before I patch it."}}
